tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE marketing_data (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id INT,
  click_through_rate FLOAT,
  conversion_rate FLOAT,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE click_data (
    click_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT NOT NULL,
    click_timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    page_id INT NOT NULL,
    click_through_rate FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE conversion_data (
    conversion_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT NOT NULL,
    conversion_timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    conversion_value DECIMAL NOT NULL,
    conversion_success BOOLEAN,
    campaign_id INT
);

CREATE TABLE click_data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    click_time TIMESTAMP,
    user_id INT,
    page_id INT,
    click_through_rate DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE conversion_data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    conversion_time TIMESTAMP,
    user_id INT,
    page_id INT,
    conversion_rate DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE click_through_rates (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    product_id INT,
    click_count INT,
    click_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE conversion_data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    product_id INT,
    conversion_count INT,
    conversion_date DATE
);
